# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ZerveChurn — .gitignore
#
# NOTE: data + model artefacts (*.parquet, *.csv, *.pkl) are intentionally
# tracked in this repo because they are needed to reproduce / audit the
# pipeline locally. The ensemble bundle (`ensemble_models.pkl`, ~6 MB) and
# the raw event log (`user_retention.parquet`, ~50 MB) are committed at the
# repo root. If you ever want to stop tracking them, uncomment the patterns
# at the bottom of this file.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Python bytecode / build artefacts ────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
.coverage.*
htmlcov/

# ── Virtual environments ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
.python-version

# ── Notebook scratch ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ── Editor / IDE configs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── OS / desktop junk ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Anaconda / Zerve workspace artefacts ─────────────────────────────────────
anaconda_projects/db/
.anaconda/

# ── Local-replay checkpoint state (very large: ~16 GB of pickled namespaces) ─
outputs/_state/
outputs/_state/**

# ── Log / error captures from local canvas runs ──────────────────────────────
# (the existing _run_*.log / _run_*.err files in outputs/ ARE tracked as
#  evidence per docs/repo_state_and_next_steps.md §1.4 — we only ignore
#  *future* large dumps that haven't been audited.)
outputs/*.tmp
outputs/*.bak

# ── Empty per-block matplotlib output folders ────────────────────────────────
# (kept on disk for the local runner to write into; only their content is
#  tracked when present.)

# ── Secrets / credentials ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
aws_credentials*
.aws/

# ── Misc temp ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.tmp
*.bak
*.log.lock

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional — uncomment to stop tracking heavy data / model artefacts.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# user_retention.parquet
# *.parquet
# user_segments.csv
# user_intelligence_export.csv
# ensemble_models.pkl
# *.pkl
